U02FG37FPSR.message:
What a week!  It's all still sinking in...

@Ali Rizvi one of your off-the-cuff comments about <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surprisingly_popular|Surprisingly Popular> probably saved me months of experimentation.  And generally for sharing your gigabrain. Can't wait for your junto! :)

@Renata Morais @Jana Cleuren @DAOrayaki our conversation was such a comfortable and safe space for me.  So calm and non-judgemental. I felt really connected to you, and by extension to the whole kernel gang.  Will always be happy to talk to you.

@Jason Mah @Kokeb Solomon @Sertac Guven @Diogo Jorge you all opened up to me in a way that let me open up to you too, and that means a lot since I'm still learning to trust people again.

@Joel Ponce @Paul Gadi @Shannon Dora thanks for letting me quiz you about game design stuff --  and your patience with my naive and persistent attempts to reach for connections to tokenomics.  Those examples you dug up for me opened up a lot of new territory.

@Danny Gattas @David Nage @Vivek Singh confidence boosters!  you helped me see where I can trust my instincts, and break through the hesitation from feeling out of my league around all these brilliant people!

@cryptowanderer seeing you in action, you've become a role model for me so quickly. how to treat people with kindness in every response, and communicate on a deeply empathetic level. makes me want to treat everyone in my life with such care.

Isn't this such a wonderful place! :smile:

